          <h1 className="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-4">
            Transform Your Space<br />Into a Green Paradise
          </h1>
          <p className="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
            Professional landscape design and execution for rooftops, balconies, and open areas in Daltonganj.
